		  	<ul>
		  	&ndash; Tax registration documentation<br />
				&ndash; Department of Revenue filing credentials, such as e-file logins<br />
				&ndash; Bank account information (name/address) for the account used to fund your sales tax liabilities
				</ul>
				<p>Note: To start filing in a given month, you must complete all setup activities by the 25<sup>th</sup> of the preceding month. For example, if you want to start filing in November, you must complete all setup activities by the 25<sup>th</sup> of October.</p>
			</div>
		</div>

