		  	<p>Keep these key dates on your calendar:</p>
		  	<ul>
			  	&ndash; Review and approve each tax return between the 5<sup>th</sup> and 10<sup>th</sup> of the month in which you’re required to file<br />
			  	&ndash; Avalara withdraws money to fund returns between the 11<sup>th</sup> and 15<sup>th</sup> of each month<br />
			  	&ndash; Avalara will then automatically file each return between the 11<sup>th</sup> and 20<sup>th</sup> of each month
